Package registration

Class Registration

  • Object
    • Registration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class Registration
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a Registration entry created in the registration database. A registration entry contains information related to the registration of a student to a camp, such as role, name of student, name of camp, and whether he has deregistered before.
    Since:
    2023-11-17
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Soo Qi Yang, Teo Kai Xuan, Masagca Merwyn Louie Dumasis, Nguyen Phuong Linh, Tee Jeeng Yee
